1
00:00:07,500 --> 00:00:08,640
I told you

2
00:00:10,390 --> 00:00:12,170
not to walk around.

3
00:00:18,710 --> 00:00:19,590
I'm sorry.

4
00:00:21,760 --> 00:00:23,160
I didn't mean to see this.

5
00:00:38,300 --> 00:00:38,700
Hyung.

6
00:00:38,750 --> 00:00:39,680
Let's talk.

7
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:45,940
Hyung, let's talk.

8
00:00:52,110 --> 00:00:52,570
No need.

9
00:00:55,040 --> 00:00:55,730
Now,

10
00:00:57,420 --> 00:00:59,680
I'm going to teach you what you should do.

11
00:01:29,450 --> 00:01:30,250
That's right.

12
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:34,000
You should've been a good boy like this.

13
00:05:38,730 --> 00:05:39,930
I can't do it anymore.

14
00:05:54,310 --> 00:05:55,140
I'm sorry.

15
00:05:57,280 --> 00:05:58,990
I didn't mean it.

16
00:06:02,150 --> 00:06:03,260
Maybe I'm afraid

17
00:06:04,450 --> 00:06:05,920
of losing you.

18
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:12,730
Especially when I saw you
hugging that teddy bear

19
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:14,200
looking at the photo,

20
00:06:17,770 --> 00:06:18,660
I was afraid

21
00:06:20,350 --> 00:06:23,350
you would leave me
after knowing everything about me—

22
00:06:23,910 --> 00:06:25,310
just like that woman did.

23
00:06:29,630 --> 00:06:31,180
I can't handle

24
00:06:31,180 --> 00:06:32,980
being abandoned again, Haejun.

25
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:35,080
Really.

26
00:06:46,950 --> 00:06:48,280
Tell me about your past.

27
00:06:51,790 --> 00:06:53,390
I won't leave you

28
00:06:55,900 --> 00:06:57,630
because you were once injured.

29
00:07:04,530 --> 00:07:06,260
I won't leave you after knowing

30
00:07:07,730 --> 00:07:08,530
your sad past.

31
00:07:09,660 --> 00:07:10,360
But

32
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:12,380
if you continue to keep it to yourself

33
00:07:12,380 --> 00:07:15,480
and hurt me as a way to vent
your fear,

34
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:17,790
our relationship won't last long.

35
00:07:33,230 --> 00:07:35,290
I'll try to understand all your pain.

36
00:07:37,970 --> 00:07:38,870
So...

37
00:07:41,220 --> 00:07:42,280
You should also...

38
00:07:46,960 --> 00:07:48,560
think about how

39
00:07:50,690 --> 00:07:52,690
we can get rid of this fear together.

40
00:07:58,270 --> 00:07:59,330
That teddy bear...

41
00:08:01,570 --> 00:08:04,230
was a Christmas gift
from my mom when I was young.

42
00:08:12,450 --> 00:08:14,510
She said even if she wasn't by my side,

43
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,690
the teddy bear would always be with me.

44
00:08:21,470 --> 00:08:22,440
After that,

45
00:08:25,380 --> 00:08:28,580
my mother couldn't handle
the domestic violence anymore

46
00:08:35,299 --> 00:08:36,650
and ran away from home.

47
00:08:39,760 --> 00:08:41,159
I should be happy for her.

48
00:08:44,700 --> 00:08:46,500
Then I went to look for my father,

49
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:49,080
really wanting to kill him,

50
00:08:49,850 --> 00:08:52,040
carrying this teddy bear.

51
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:54,620
I cried and shouted,

52
00:08:55,550 --> 00:08:57,150
asking him where my mom went.

53
00:08:59,650 --> 00:09:00,870
But my father

54
00:09:03,580 --> 00:09:05,710
threw the teddy bear into the trash can

55
00:09:08,230 --> 00:09:09,690
and locked me in the attic.

56
00:09:12,620 --> 00:09:14,620
The appearance of the teddy bear...

57
00:09:15,410 --> 00:09:16,110
No.

58
00:09:17,140 --> 00:09:18,480
Your appearance

59
00:09:19,710 --> 00:09:22,510
makes me feel like
I've found the teddy bear again.

60
00:09:26,060 --> 00:09:27,980
So I want to keep you by my side.

61
00:09:29,460 --> 00:09:31,060
I don't want to lose you.

62
00:09:34,820 --> 00:09:37,080
I'm afraid of being alone again, Haejun.

63
00:09:40,570 --> 00:09:42,630
I'm afraid you'll leave me like my mom

64
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:46,000
after knowing everything.

65
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:51,850
I don't want to taste failure again

66
00:09:53,500 --> 00:09:55,170
through that bear.

67
00:09:59,120 --> 00:09:59,920
You're wrong.

68
00:10:01,850 --> 00:10:02,980
You are like this...

69
00:10:05,180 --> 00:10:07,310
only because you've never been loved.

70
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,940
Let's learn together.

71
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:15,670
I won't leave you.

72
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:19,410
But...

73
00:10:22,970 --> 00:10:25,630
if you want to
shoulder that suffering alone...

74
00:10:52,450 --> 00:10:52,920
Let me

75
00:10:53,490 --> 00:10:54,090
untie you.

76
00:10:55,280 --> 00:10:55,790
No.

77
00:10:58,010 --> 00:10:58,720
It's okay.

78
00:11:02,040 --> 00:11:03,170
I'll keep wearing it

79
00:11:05,330 --> 00:11:06,730
until you've recovered.

80
00:11:09,420 --> 00:11:11,660
Until you learn how to love,

81
00:11:13,740 --> 00:11:14,970
I will be wearing it.

82
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,440
Take it as a token of our love.

83
00:11:21,630 --> 00:11:22,520
Keep it.

84
00:11:27,630 --> 00:11:28,200
Promise.

85
00:11:45,570 --> 00:11:47,570
[I already know Jaehun's past.
Thank you, Soohyuk. I'll help him
get rid of his childhood trauma.]

86
00:11:49,410 --> 00:11:52,420
[I already know Jaehun's past.
Thank you, Soohyuk. I'll help him
get rid of his childhood trauma.]

87
00:11:54,100 --> 00:11:54,760
Kim Haejun.

88
00:12:00,580 --> 00:12:01,710
So you've found out?

89
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,690
And you want to help him with it?

90
00:12:10,100 --> 00:12:12,810
How naive.

91
00:12:41,290 --> 00:12:42,120
Hey, Jaehun.

92
00:12:43,310 --> 00:12:44,370
Let's have a drink.

93
00:12:57,330 --> 00:12:58,060
You're here.

94
00:13:16,820 --> 00:13:18,120
I came because you told me
something important came up.

95
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:18,740
Shoot.

96
00:13:19,470 --> 00:13:20,400
I need to go back.

97
00:13:21,030 --> 00:13:21,730
Why?

98
00:13:21,860 --> 00:13:24,320
Are you going back
to take care of Kim Haejun?

99
00:13:24,400 --> 00:13:26,530
You used to stay up all night and drink.

100
00:13:27,180 --> 00:13:30,580
You just got here and
you're thinking about leaving already?

101
00:13:31,580 --> 00:13:32,040
Jaehun.

102
00:13:32,970 --> 00:13:34,700
Do you know what you've become?

103
00:13:34,820 --> 00:13:36,620
You're completely bound by him.

104
00:13:38,560 --> 00:13:39,900
Who knows

105
00:13:41,070 --> 00:13:42,530
who's the one being bound?

106
00:13:43,810 --> 00:13:45,090
How confident.

107
00:13:48,980 --> 00:13:50,070
I really want to see

108
00:13:50,170 --> 00:13:51,170
when you are down.

109
00:13:55,190 --> 00:13:56,610
Just imagine it.

110
00:14:05,400 --> 00:14:06,100
By the way,

111
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:07,870
a few days ago,

112
00:14:07,870 --> 00:14:09,130
Yoon Minwoo called me.

113
00:14:11,500 --> 00:14:13,700
He's now a certified physiotherapist.

114
00:14:17,920 --> 00:14:19,540
He majored in architecture,

115
00:14:18,220 --> 00:14:20,740
[Physiotherapist Yoon Minwoo]

116
00:14:19,690 --> 00:14:21,840
but now he's suddenly a physiotherapist.

117
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:22,800
I asked him why,

118
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:24,400
but he didn't answer.

119
00:14:27,800 --> 00:14:28,600
Could it be...

120
00:14:29,350 --> 00:14:30,240
for you?

121
00:14:33,460 --> 00:14:34,620
You studied architecture,

122
00:14:34,620 --> 00:14:35,480
so he followed.

123
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:38,000
He heard you have a mental illness,

124
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:40,000
so he got trained in physiotherapy.

125
00:14:40,290 --> 00:14:41,390
He's so loyal.

126
00:14:46,140 --> 00:14:48,400
I don't understand why he's so annoying.

127
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:51,760
But you two know each other well.

128
00:14:53,070 --> 00:14:54,130
Isn't that better?

129
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:57,130
Given your state recently,

130
00:14:57,340 --> 00:14:58,270
you need someone by your side

131
00:14:58,270 --> 00:14:59,630
to take care of you.

132
00:15:01,040 --> 00:15:04,100
It's better than
looking for another doctor out there.

133
00:15:04,480 --> 00:15:05,690
Especially since

134
00:15:06,670 --> 00:15:08,330
you're so out of focus lately.

135
00:15:16,250 --> 00:15:16,840
Okay.

136
00:15:17,850 --> 00:15:18,850
I'll contact him.

137
00:16:09,660 --> 00:16:10,530
You're back.

138
00:16:12,030 --> 00:16:13,480
I came back quickly, right?

139
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:13,920
Yes.

140
00:16:17,030 --> 00:16:18,960
I need to finish reading this book.

141
00:16:19,670 --> 00:16:21,470
This is tomorrow's assignment.

142
00:16:22,330 --> 00:16:22,760
No.

143
00:16:23,710 --> 00:16:25,770
Why would someone asleep
be reading?

144
00:16:26,320 --> 00:16:27,280
Read it tomorrow.

145
00:16:27,280 --> 00:16:27,620
Okay?

146
00:16:28,220 --> 00:16:30,280
Reading at night is bad for your eyes.

147
00:16:33,610 --> 00:16:34,670
More importantly,

148
00:16:35,940 --> 00:16:37,140
if you're not sleepy,

149
00:16:37,480 --> 00:16:38,940
shall we do something fun?

150
00:16:39,230 --> 00:16:40,830
I'm sleepy.

151
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:41,950
Gosh.

152
00:16:45,700 --> 00:16:46,300
Okay.

153
00:16:54,300 --> 00:16:55,430
Good night, my baby.

154
00:16:55,650 --> 00:16:56,680
I'm going to take a shower.

155
00:16:56,680 --> 00:16:57,010
Okay.

156
00:17:18,030 --> 00:17:20,990
[Physiotherapist,
Yoon Minwoo]

157
00:17:22,910 --> 00:17:23,589
Oh, right.

158
00:17:24,470 --> 00:17:25,180
A few days ago,

159
00:17:25,180 --> 00:17:26,440
Yoon Minwoo called me.

160
00:17:29,040 --> 00:17:31,240
He's now a certified physiotherapist.

161
00:18:12,850 --> 00:18:14,510
I gave him your business card.

162
00:18:15,130 --> 00:18:15,460
Okay.

163
00:18:15,520 --> 00:18:15,940
But...

164
00:18:17,530 --> 00:18:19,330
why don't you go to him yourself?

165
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:21,380
You keep making me the messenger.

166
00:18:23,090 --> 00:18:23,550
Minwoo.

167
00:18:24,460 --> 00:18:26,660
When are you going to change that habit?

168
00:18:27,320 --> 00:18:29,450
If you like him, go after him yourself.

169
00:18:31,580 --> 00:18:33,310
How many years has it been?

170
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:36,010
Is this love?

171
00:18:37,890 --> 00:18:38,340
Yes.

172
00:18:39,540 --> 00:18:40,140
Are you...

173
00:18:41,090 --> 00:18:41,640
shy?

174
00:18:43,270 --> 00:18:43,880
No.

175
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:46,450
I just

176
00:18:48,290 --> 00:18:49,750
don't know on what grounds

177
00:18:50,770 --> 00:18:51,700
I should meet him

178
00:18:53,280 --> 00:18:54,210
as.

179
00:18:59,420 --> 00:19:00,800
Jaehun is a good person.

180
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:03,790
Can I

181
00:19:05,470 --> 00:19:06,280
be with him?

182
00:19:10,470 --> 00:19:12,460
I've known him for so long.

183
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:15,810
But I've never gotten tired of him.

184
00:19:18,710 --> 00:19:19,160
Then

185
00:19:19,760 --> 00:19:20,290
go to him.

186
00:19:22,250 --> 00:19:24,310
Isn't he the person you want the most?

187
00:19:26,070 --> 00:19:28,070
He needs help now.

188
00:19:28,780 --> 00:19:29,980
And you're an expert.

189
00:19:31,010 --> 00:19:32,940
Is there a better reason than that?

190
00:19:34,550 --> 00:19:35,740
You're just like that

191
00:19:35,740 --> 00:19:37,270
just because of Kim Haejun.

192
00:19:38,930 --> 00:19:39,990
From what I can see,

193
00:19:40,580 --> 00:19:41,840
Kim Haejun is just a toy

194
00:19:42,150 --> 00:19:43,550
he fell momentarily for.

195
00:19:45,030 --> 00:19:47,030
He'll get sick of it sooner or later.

196
00:19:49,840 --> 00:19:52,020
Your friendship of over 20 years

197
00:19:53,810 --> 00:19:55,070
is stronger than that.

198
00:20:25,130 --> 00:20:25,990
Kang Soohyung.

199
00:20:28,050 --> 00:20:28,890
You're right.

200
00:20:32,720 --> 00:20:34,050
This is an opportunity.

201
00:20:36,520 --> 00:20:37,380
I won't miss out

202
00:20:38,250 --> 00:20:39,450
on this opportunity.

203
00:20:42,020 --> 00:20:42,660
Nice.

204
00:20:44,420 --> 00:20:45,820
I'm looking forward

205
00:20:46,270 --> 00:20:47,530
to how it will turn out.

206
00:21:26,090 --> 00:21:28,220
What kind of sleeping posture is this?

207
00:22:17,740 --> 00:22:18,710
Am I dreaming?

208
00:22:21,690 --> 00:22:22,330
Yes.

209
00:22:23,520 --> 00:22:24,990
You're dreaming.

210
00:22:32,840 --> 00:22:35,640
Yes, you're dreaming.

211
00:23:28,460 --> 00:23:29,520
What are you doing?

212
00:23:31,180 --> 00:23:32,330
I'm hanging this up.

213
00:23:33,090 --> 00:23:34,150
This is mistletoe.

214
00:23:36,240 --> 00:23:37,200
A mistletoe?

215
00:23:38,880 --> 00:23:39,610
What's that?

216
00:23:40,330 --> 00:23:41,160
Is it a plant?

217
00:23:42,330 --> 00:23:43,130
This is a plant

218
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:45,590
you hang up on Christmas.

219
00:23:46,840 --> 00:23:48,920
Legend has it that couples
who kiss under it

220
00:23:48,920 --> 00:23:51,270
will be together forever.

221
00:23:56,040 --> 00:23:56,750
Then,

222
00:23:59,740 --> 00:24:01,000
what if I do it this way?

223
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:14,230
You learn so quickly.

224
00:24:15,880 --> 00:24:16,520
Well,

225
00:24:17,310 --> 00:24:19,230
unlike a certain bad student.

226
00:24:20,860 --> 00:24:22,010
Are you mocking me?

227
00:24:23,260 --> 00:24:24,160
No.

228
00:24:25,220 --> 00:24:26,820
You're going to hang this up?

229
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:28,370
Do you want me to carry you?

230
00:24:28,370 --> 00:24:28,820
Yes.

231
00:24:33,840 --> 00:24:34,360
One.

232
00:24:34,360 --> 00:24:34,840
Two.

233
00:24:34,840 --> 00:24:35,280
Three.

234
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:48,420
It is said that

235
00:24:49,440 --> 00:24:50,840
lovers can ask for kisses

236
00:24:51,600 --> 00:24:52,800
under the mistletoe.

237
00:24:56,070 --> 00:24:56,680
I am asking

238
00:24:57,100 --> 00:24:57,700
for a kiss.

239
00:25:01,530 --> 00:25:02,740
I won't refuse.

240
00:26:19,810 --> 00:26:20,450
You are...

241
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:23,120
Hello.

242
00:26:24,150 --> 00:26:25,480
I'm a physiotherapist.

243
00:26:27,020 --> 00:26:27,880
Is Jaehun here?

244
00:26:28,780 --> 00:26:29,840
Physiotherapist?

245
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:37,150
Jaehun.

246
00:26:38,750 --> 00:26:41,410
Why did you suddenly become
a physiotherapist?

247
00:26:41,610 --> 00:26:42,400
Come in, Minwoo.

248
00:26:42,400 --> 00:26:42,730
Okay.

249
00:26:51,760 --> 00:26:52,780
What's going on?

250
00:26:53,710 --> 00:26:55,310
I'm getting some treatment.

251
00:26:55,870 --> 00:26:57,070
I need to get well soon

252
00:26:57,280 --> 00:26:58,880
so that I won't hurt you more.

253
00:26:59,690 --> 00:27:00,620
Will you be fine?

254
00:27:02,430 --> 00:27:03,830
Are you worried about me?

255
00:27:10,840 --> 00:27:12,240
I'll take care of myself.

256
00:27:13,460 --> 00:27:14,350
My baby.

257
00:27:16,180 --> 00:27:16,950
Okay.

258
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:18,790
As long as your body is fine.

259
00:27:18,790 --> 00:27:19,520
Just my body?

260
00:27:20,040 --> 00:27:21,170
Yes, just your body.

261
00:27:21,580 --> 00:27:22,990
Don't worry. I'll go for my treatment.

262
00:27:22,990 --> 00:27:23,260
Okay.

263
00:27:23,260 --> 00:27:24,660
-Call me anytime.
-Okay.

264
00:27:45,930 --> 00:27:47,530
Your muscles are very tight.

265
00:27:49,310 --> 00:27:51,440
Are you under a lot of stress recently?

266
00:27:51,930 --> 00:27:52,660
Or do you have

267
00:27:53,320 --> 00:27:54,520
bad sleeping habits?

268
00:27:56,370 --> 00:27:58,370
Maybe I haven't been sleeping well.

269
00:27:59,320 --> 00:28:02,520
I heard you refused the marriage
arranged by your family.

270
00:28:02,830 --> 00:28:04,660
Your dad is quite angry.

271
00:28:07,750 --> 00:28:08,900
She seems nice.

272
00:28:11,060 --> 00:28:12,460
We met a few times before.

273
00:28:15,700 --> 00:28:17,430
Are you here to be a matchmaker?

274
00:28:18,780 --> 00:28:19,670
No.

275
00:28:20,280 --> 00:28:20,980
I just

276
00:28:22,740 --> 00:28:23,610
hope

277
00:28:24,130 --> 00:28:25,850
you can meet someone

278
00:28:27,200 --> 00:28:28,400
who suits you better.

279
00:28:37,690 --> 00:28:38,850
Leave me alone.

280
00:28:39,310 --> 00:28:41,310
Just worry about your own marriage.

281
00:28:44,380 --> 00:28:46,040
Was that your new bed partner?

282
00:28:46,450 --> 00:28:47,310
He looks young.

283
00:28:48,420 --> 00:28:49,280
Is he a student?

284
00:28:50,880 --> 00:28:52,140
That's very different

285
00:28:52,940 --> 00:28:54,340
from your past partners.

286
00:28:57,030 --> 00:28:59,160
Do you remember when you were younger?

287
00:28:59,680 --> 00:29:00,890
I was worried

288
00:29:01,400 --> 00:29:02,800
your dad would scold you,

289
00:29:02,850 --> 00:29:04,710
so I'd say I'm staying for dinner.

290
00:29:09,050 --> 00:29:09,850
That's right.

291
00:29:11,290 --> 00:29:12,750
Back then, in my dad's eyes

292
00:29:13,680 --> 00:29:15,360
you were just a beggar who'd always

293
00:29:15,360 --> 00:29:16,890
come for meals at our place.

294
00:29:19,870 --> 00:29:21,540
But thankfully I was around.

295
00:29:23,380 --> 00:29:24,270
Since then,

296
00:29:28,370 --> 00:29:29,050
I thought of

297
00:29:29,510 --> 00:29:30,370
protecting you

298
00:29:32,840 --> 00:29:34,000
as my duty.

299
00:29:36,060 --> 00:29:36,790
Even now too.

300
00:29:40,020 --> 00:29:41,350
No matter what happens,

301
00:29:44,440 --> 00:29:45,640
I will be by your side.

302
00:29:47,140 --> 00:29:47,680
Okay.

303
00:29:48,300 --> 00:29:48,900
Thank you.

304
00:30:11,170 --> 00:30:11,730
It's over?

305
00:30:11,730 --> 00:30:11,990
Yes.

306
00:30:30,550 --> 00:30:31,480
Have a good rest.

307
00:30:32,900 --> 00:30:33,640
I'll come again

308
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:34,240
next time.

309
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:36,200
See you next time.

310
00:30:54,870 --> 00:30:55,580
Wow.

311
00:30:55,580 --> 00:30:56,520
My artist.

312
00:30:56,910 --> 00:30:58,280
You've improved a lot.

313
00:30:59,450 --> 00:31:00,090
Hyung,

314
00:31:00,640 --> 00:31:01,990
are you making fun of me?

315
00:31:04,270 --> 00:31:04,900
By the way,

316
00:31:06,020 --> 00:31:08,640
the person who just left
is called Yoon Minwoo, right?

317
00:31:08,640 --> 00:31:10,640
What's your relationship with him?

318
00:31:14,170 --> 00:31:15,050
Minwoo and I

319
00:31:16,120 --> 00:31:17,980
are neighbors and friends.

320
00:31:19,250 --> 00:31:20,410
We grew up together.

321
00:31:20,960 --> 00:31:22,620
We just got in touch recently.

322
00:31:23,650 --> 00:31:26,860
I heard he's an expert,
so I'm receiving treatment from him.

323
00:31:26,860 --> 00:31:27,310
I see.

324
00:31:28,010 --> 00:31:28,610
But

325
00:31:30,520 --> 00:31:32,450
the way he looks at me is different.

326
00:31:32,770 --> 00:31:34,630
Are you hiding something from me?

327
00:31:36,470 --> 00:31:38,530
We've been friends since childhood.

328
00:31:39,120 --> 00:31:40,270
We grew up together.

329
00:31:41,360 --> 00:31:43,020
We just got in touch recently.

330
00:31:43,080 --> 00:31:44,810
He's an expert,
so I'm receiving treatment from him.

331
00:31:44,810 --> 00:31:46,200
That's all.

332
00:31:49,980 --> 00:31:50,780
As long as

333
00:31:51,870 --> 00:31:54,440
it's good for you,
everything's great.

334
00:31:55,650 --> 00:31:57,780
When you're having classes,
I can call him over

335
00:31:57,780 --> 00:31:59,040
and introduce you two.

336
00:31:59,140 --> 00:31:59,800
How's that?

337
00:31:59,930 --> 00:32:00,930
I don't want that.

338
00:32:01,100 --> 00:32:01,800
Me neither.

339
00:32:10,280 --> 00:32:11,010
What is this?

340
00:32:13,930 --> 00:32:14,960
I just bought it.

341
00:32:16,560 --> 00:32:17,690
The previous one

342
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:18,800
was too heavy

343
00:32:18,800 --> 00:32:20,660
and too exposed. I didn't like it.

344
00:32:21,870 --> 00:32:23,360
I don't even feel this one.

345
00:32:24,520 --> 00:32:25,050
Your name

346
00:32:25,260 --> 00:32:26,620
is on the necklace too.

347
00:32:34,400 --> 00:32:35,350
Thank you.

348
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:37,970
Kiss me if you're thankful.

349
00:33:04,820 --> 00:33:18,270
[Tide of Love 2]

350
00:34:38,110 --> 00:34:45,989
[Tide of Love 2]
